iry Free Overnight Oats<br />\n有無人知減唔減到肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n午餐：citysuper 燒春雞set配菜<br />\n<br />\n今晚體脂計送到屋企可以磅下自己有幾肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b0853388f88bf3384b8a07180990d93ea6e8a0","tid":625110,"uid":68033,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4270eee0d5a0fdeb433b5206c2f36ff529825d4b","tid":625110,"uid":75964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T07:43:12.000Z","msg":"2018/04/11<br />\n<br />\n晚餐：向屋企食所以全部都好清<br />\n菜一碗、雞肉四舊<br />\n夜晚不嬲唔係好食飯<br />\n<br />\n2018/04/12<br />\n早餐：Pret a manger既Dairy Free Overnight Oats<br />\n有無人知減唔減到肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n午餐：citysuper 燒春雞set配菜<br />\n<br />\n今晚體脂計送到屋企可以磅下自己有幾肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T08:04:08.000Z","msg":"減唔減到肥最主要睇每日吸收<br />\n要計自己嘅TDEE<br />\n例如計到TDEE係2500<br />\n咁你每日淨係食2000-2400 <br />\n每日都有熱量赤字就會慢慢變輕<br />\n<br />\n所以OATS話就係健康食物<br />\n主要係因為佢營養均衡同埋又有纖維同唔同維他命<br />\n但係熱量都唔少 食得多一樣會變重"},{"pid":"ffec645c50c9db5b969afd4c2a9290f03b3bb7bb","tid":625110,"uid":37245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T08:33:36.000Z","msg":"我又開始減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n目標30磅<br />\n<br />\n一齊集氣"},{"pid":"09dcfc6eb8f0896d54e1e479bc5667e40b63444a","tid":625110,"uid":129573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T15:23:00.000Z","msg":"你食太少<br />\n一食返多好易反彈<br />\n三街出街食照減到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c92bd6503be23550acdbfc159ca69548299ba0ea","tid":62